<h2 id='delete-a-product'>Delete a product</h2>
<p>This API lets you delete a product variant.</p>
<h3 id='http-request-5'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>DELETE /api/v1/products/{product}/variants/{variant}</code></p>
